Wiltshire Council £4.25m&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id="larger-bids"&gt;Larger bids&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bristol City Council £24m&lt;br&gt;
Bournemouth Borough Council £12.1m&lt;br&gt;
